<h2 id="how-to-contact-the-data-protection-officer">How to contact the Data Protection Officer</h2>

<p>Contact our Data Protection Officer (<abbr title="Data Protection Officer">DPO</abbr>) with any concerns about how we or our services handle your personal information.</p>

<p id="dpo">The <abbr title="Data Protection Officer">DPO</abbr> is responsible for independent advice and monitoring how <abbr title="Department Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy">BEIS</abbr> uses personal information.</p>

